cs.NA, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SI 

The paper deals with a numerical linear algebra technique (SVD) and uses information theory to determine the optimal rank. Therefore, it is likely to belong to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses simulation experiments, which suggests it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
